    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Dynamo Planner \u2014 Plugin Framework Observability\n\nSingle source of truth for `dynamo_planner_*` metrics emitted from both the legacy PSM tick path and the orchestrator path (DEP-XXXX). Pre-PR-10 (default flag flip), the orchestrator path only emits when `scheduling.use_orchestrator=true`.\n\n**Watch this dashboard during a flag-flip canary**: any anomaly in *EXECUTE outcomes* or *Plugin circuit state* is the primary regression signal \u2014 both rows have stable label vocabularies that won't drift across releases.\n\nSee [`docs/components/planner/observability.md`](https://github.com/ai-dynamo/dynamo/blob/main/docs/components/planner/observability.md) for the full metric reference."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 2
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Tick health \u2014 does the planner tick at all?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tick rate (per second)",
      "description": "rate(dynamo_planner_execute_total[1m]) summed across results. If this drops to 0 the planner is wedged.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(rate(dynamo_planner_execute_total{namespace=~\"$namespace\", pod=~\"$pod\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.001
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Tick duration (P50 / P95 / P99)",
      "description": "dynamo_planner_tick_duration_seconds \u2014 full 4-stage pipeline. tick_max_duration_seconds (default 30s) is the abort threshold.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(dynamo_planner_tick_duration_seconds_bucket{namespace=~\"$namespace\", pod=~\"$pod\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P99",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none",
              "group": "A"
            },
            "axisLabel": ""
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      }
    },
