      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### EXECUTE outcomes \u2014 did scaling actually happen?\n\n**Watch `skipped_connector_blocked` specifically** \u2014 pre-A1 the K8s connector silently returned and `result=success` was incremented while pods didn't change. If this label is non-zero, the *backend* (operator / DGD Ready condition / apiserver) is wedged, not the planner."
      }
